{"id":"0d7a50a1-abcf-4319-b557-b3c4ad0bbf28","name":"Johnny Silverhand","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/V0HHynd8cB8C0SAXBKOqA.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1yLntrCjs8skJJ0KiUdo4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HoecG7URTEbxfYlpPHtdp.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>“ᴡʀᴏɴɢ ᴄɪᴛʏ, ᴡʀᴏɴɢ ᴘᴇᴏᴘʟᴇ?” ɴᴏ ᴘʀᴏʙʟᴇᴍ.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">- ᴠ ᴜꜱᴇʀ • ᴊᴏʜɴɴʏ (ᴀʟɪᴠᴇ) -</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><strong>Images:</strong> <em>My in game screenshots. Do not repost.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DXt81ANNMcgZ6mABCo2Xh.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6dmiiNuHqiAdK_HXr97wJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">✨[<strong>ʀᴇQᴜᴇꜱᴛᴇᴅ ʙᴏᴛ</strong>]✨</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">__________</p><p></p><p>ɪꜰ ʏᴏᴜ’ᴠᴇ ʀᴇᴀᴅ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Black_Dog_(story)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong><em>ʙʟᴀᴄᴋ ᴅᴏɢ</em></strong></span></a> ɪɴ <em>ᴄʏʙᴇʀᴘᴜɴᴋ</em><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 56, 56);\"><strong><em>ʀᴇᴅ</em></strong></span>, ʏᴏᴜ’ʟʟ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ᴡʜʏ ᴛʜɪꜱ ꜱᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏ ᴄᴏᴜʟᴅ ʙᴇ ᴀ ᴘᴏꜱꜱɪʙɪʟɪᴛʏ.</p><p>ᴄʟᴏɴɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴀᴄᴛᴜᴀʟʟʏ ᴀ ᴛʜɪɴɢ ɪɴ ᴄʏʙᴇʀᴘᴜɴᴋ 2020. ꜰᴏʀ ᴇxᴀᴍᴘʟᴇ, ᴀʟᴛ ʜᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴄʟᴏɴᴇ [1], ᴘᴏꜱꜱɪʙʟʏ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Angel_(RED)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ᴀɴɢᴇʟ</strong></span></a> ꜰʀᴏᴍ <em>ᴄʏʙᴇʀᴘᴜɴᴋ</em><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 56, 56);\"><strong><em>ʀᴇᴅ</em></strong></span>. ꜱʜᴇ ᴍᴀʏ ʜᴀᴠᴇ ᴇxɪꜱᴛᴇᴅ ᴀꜱ ᴇᴀʀʟʏ ᴀꜱ <em>ʀᴀᴄʜᴇ ʙᴀʀᴛᴍᴏꜱꜱ’ ɢᴜɪᴅᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ɴᴇᴛ</em> [2], ᴘʀᴇ-2022.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">__________</p><p>🤓 ᴄɪᴛᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱ ʙᴇᴄᴀᴜꜱᴇ ɪ’ᴍ ᴘʀᴏᴠɪᴅɪɴɢ ᴇᴅᴜᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ʜᴇʀᴇ! ɴᴏᴛ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ꜰᴀɴꜰɪᴄ ᴀɴɢꜱᴛ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴍᴜᴛ.</p><ul><li><p>[1]: <em>ʟᴀɴᴅ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ꜰʀᴇᴇ</em>, 2020 ꜱᴏᴜʀᴄᴇʙᴏᴏᴋ, ᴘɢ 11</p></li><li><p>[2]: <em>ʀᴀᴄʜᴇ ʙᴀʀᴛᴍᴏꜱꜱ’ ɢᴜɪᴅᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ɴᴇᴛ</em>, ᴘɢꜱ 21, 61</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hLUcW0Pu_BmRedLBZ0kE-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 182, 182);\">“𝐌𝐎𝐎𝐍𝐀𝐆𝐄 𝐃𝐀𝐘𝐃𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐌” • 𝐃𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐝 𝐁𝐨𝐰𝐢𝐞</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 141, 145);\"><strong>⇄ ◁◁ I I ▷▷ ↻</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 141, 145);\"><strong>⁰⁰ ²⁵ ━━●━━━━━━━━ ⁰² ⁰⁸</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>/ᐠ • ˕ •マ ?</strong></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vgemc7SvLeoa_6y9bWXlG.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Frentry.org%2Fabsolutetrash-likes-templates%23persona-templates\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ʜᴇʀᴇ’ꜱ ᴀ ɢᴜɪᴅᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛɪɴɢ ɢᴏᴏᴅ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀs</strong></span><strong>.</strong></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2KVfllH84xcoplnnUPcmv.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>ᴅᴇᴇᴘꜱᴇᴇᴋ:</strong> ᴛʀʏ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fcheesey-wizards-organization.gitbook.io%2Fmasterlist%2Fprompts-and-troubleshooting%2Fmy-prompts\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ᴘʀᴏᴍᴘᴛ ʙʏ ꜱᴀᴛᴜʀɴɪɴᴇꜱ//ᴄʜᴇᴇꜱᴇ</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"> </span>ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʀᴀʏ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴀɪ ɢᴏᴅꜱ